<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- mḥbẗ rby btdwb qlby dy mḥbẗ ʿjybẗ wmạ lyhạ nẓyr
 mḥbẗ tḥyr lmạ tgẖyr ḥạl ạlʿbd fybqy̱ ạ̉myr
 1- mḥbẗ tfyḍ ʿly̱ kl ạlnạs byḍ ạ̉w swd kl ạlạ̉jnạs
 lmạ ạldm bybqy̱ yṭhr ydy ạlkl ḥyạẗ wkẖlạṣ
 2- mḥbẗ tdwr tmsẖy bʿyd mhmạ nkwn llsẖr ʿbyd
 tfk ạlạ̉sr wtdy ạlnṣr tkẖly ạlqlb tmly sʿyd
 3- mḥbẗ mạ yʿrf bqymhạ wlạ yʿrf ʿẓmẗ klfthạ
 ạ̹lạ ạlly wfy̱ dywnh yswʿ gẖfr lh ạ̉tẖạmh bjmlthạ</lyrics>
<title>mḥbẗ rby btdẖwb qlby</title>
</song>